0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"BNO 好似幾時都去得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:54:37.000Z","msg":"Yes - BN(O) passport holders are not subject to the annual quota of 1,000 set by the UK government. BN(O) passport holders can apply for an UK Tier 5 Working Holiday visa at any time before his 31st birthday."},{"pid":"e004fedf1852363a1f19482c5ba094f53f37758e","tid":613722,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:58:44.000Z","msg":"Remember to use your BN(O) passport to get your UK Tier 5 Working Holiday visa. BN(O) passport holders do not need to register with the local police in the UK and they can register to vote in all UK elections.<br />\n<br />\nHKSAR passport holders on the other hand, as Chinese nationals, are required to register with the local police in the UK and not allow to register to vote in any elections in the UK."},{"pid":"0f19d3ac584ca47f6a5d097193a7d46feca0c816","tid":613722,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T17:30:13.000Z","msg":"Have a look at the thread below for more info - <br />\n<br />\n【英國】 英倫扮工室 XV<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/621527/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/621527/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"522c1ab936b58499f43d42e061c39b8a8b316d68","tid":613722,"uid":90605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"go together? I also want to go!! About in January"},{"pid":"c505df3a09734bbd4cd85d6b477d331a1d353d8e","tid":613722,"uid":91216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"我都去呀！ 交個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9114f2bfcd253b9f03f56def0f4b56f11174da09","tid":613722,"uid":231114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T15:34:56.000Z","msg"